{
  "book": "enos",
  "bookName": "Enos",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 429.101,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, it came to pass that I, Enos, knowing my father",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.524,
      "end": 5.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was a just man\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.562,
      "end": 7.559,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he taught me in his language,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 7.739,
      "end": 10.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in the nurture and admonition of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.123,
      "end": 13.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and blessed be the name of my God for it\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.264,
      "end": 17.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will tell you of the wrestle which I had before God,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.695,
      "end": 20.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before I received a remission of my sins.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.836,
      "end": 23.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I went to hunt beasts in the forests;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 23.988,
      "end": 27.378,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which I had often heard my father speak",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 27.558,
      "end": 29.323,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning eternal life",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 29.503,
      "end": 32.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the joy of the saints, sunk deep into my heart.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 33.666,
      "end": 35.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my soul hungered;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 35.332,
      "end": 37.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I kneeled down before my Maker,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 37.741,
      "end": 39.459,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried unto him",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 39.639,
      "end": 43.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mighty prayer and supplication for mine own soul;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 43.256,
      "end": 45.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all the day long did I cry unto him;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 45.758,
      "end": 47.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and when the night came",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 48.167,
      "end": 50.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did still raise my voice high",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 50.297,
      "end": 51.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it reached the heavens.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 52.649,
      "end": 55.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there came a voice unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 55.197,
      "end": 57.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Enos, thy sins are forgiven thee,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 57.885,
      "end": 59.51,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt be blessed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 60.19,
      "end": 62.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew that God could not lie;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 63.11,
      "end": 65.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, my guilt was swept away.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 66.158,
      "end": 68.201,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said: Lord, how is it done?",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 68.881,
      "end": 70.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said unto me:",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 70.64,
      "end": 72.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Because of thy faith in Christ,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 72.863,
      "end": 75.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom thou hast never before heard nor seen.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 75.644,
      "end": 77.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many years pass away",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 77.728,
      "end": 80.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before he shall manifest himself in the flesh;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 80.694,
      "end": 82.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, go to,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 82.453,
      "end": 84.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thy faith hath made thee whole.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 85.13,
      "end": 88.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, it came to pass that when I had heard these words",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 88.561,
      "end": 93.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to feel a desire for the welfare of my brethren, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 93.617,
      "end": 97.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I did pour out my whole soul unto God for them.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 98.105,
      "end": 101.124,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while I was thus struggling in the spirit,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 101.304,
      "end": 104.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the voice of the Lord came into my mind again, saying:",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 105.06,
      "end": 106.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will visit thy brethren",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 107.005,
      "end": 110.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to their diligence in keeping my commandments.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 110.389,
      "end": 112.525,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have given unto them this land,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 112.705,
      "end": 114.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a holy land;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 114.65,
      "end": 116.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I curse it not",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 116.502,
      "end": 119.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be for the cause of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 119.236,
      "end": 122.998,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I will visit thy brethren according as I have said;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 123.178,
      "end": 127.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their transgressions will I bring down with sorrow upon their own heads.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 128.316,
      "end": 131.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I, Enos, had heard these words,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 131.236,
      "end": 133.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my faith began to be unshaken in the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 134.11,
      "end": 139.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I prayed unto him with many long strugglings for my brethren, the Lamanites.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 139.806,
      "end": 144.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after I had prayed and labored with all diligence,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 144.305,
      "end": 145.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord said unto me:",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 146.064,
      "end": 149.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will grant unto thee according to thy desires,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 149.355,
      "end": 151.027,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of thy faith.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 151.707,
      "end": 155.283,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, this was the desire which I desired of him\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 155.463,
      "end": 157.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if it should so be",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 157.315,
      "end": 159.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my people, the Nephites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 159.399,
      "end": 161.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should fall into transgression,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 161.715,
      "end": 163.758,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by any means be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 163.938,
      "end": 166.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamanites should not be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 166.626,
      "end": 172.013,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God would preserve a record of my people, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 172.193,
      "end": 175.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be by the power of his holy arm,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 175.345,
      "end": 180.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it might be brought forth at some future day unto the Lamanites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 180.355,
      "end": 183.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that, perhaps, they might be brought unto salvation\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 184.379,
      "end": 187.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For at the present our strugglings were vain",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 187.531,
      "end": 189.899,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in restoring them to the true faith.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 190.079,
      "end": 192.169,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they swore in their wrath that,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 192.349,
      "end": 193.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it were possible,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 194.108,
      "end": 196.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would destroy our records and us,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 196.935,
      "end": 199.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all the traditions of our fathers.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 200.262,
      "end": 201.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I knowing",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 201.928,
      "end": 205.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God was able to preserve our records,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 205.219,
      "end": 208.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cried unto him continually, for he had said unto me:",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 208.65,
      "end": 211.065,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whatsoever thing ye shall ask in faith,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 211.245,
      "end": 214.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that ye shall receive in the name of Christ,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 214.536,
      "end": 216.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall receive it.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 216.795,
      "end": 218.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I had faith,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 218.415,
      "end": 220.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did cry unto God",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 220.267,
      "end": 222.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would preserve the records;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 222.49,
      "end": 224.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 224.388,
      "end": 228.614,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would bring them forth unto the Lamanites in his own due time.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 229.294,
      "end": 233.799,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew it would be according to the covenant which he had made;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 233.979,
      "end": 235.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore my soul did rest.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 236.563,
      "end": 238.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord said unto me:",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 238.508,
      "end": 241.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thy fathers have also required of me this thing;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 241.474,
      "end": 245.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall be done unto them according to their faith;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 245.23,
      "end": 248.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for their faith was like unto thine.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 248.743,
      "end": 254.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now it came to pass that I, Enos, went about among the people of Nephi,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 254.589,
      "end": 256.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying of things to come,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 256.952,
      "end": 260.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and testifying of the things which I had heard and seen.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 261.022,
      "end": 265.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record that the people of Nephi did seek diligently",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 265.939,
      "end": 269.19,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to restore the Lamanites unto the true faith in God.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 269.37,
      "end": 271.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But our labors were vain;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 271.593,
      "end": 273.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their hatred was fixed,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 273.398,
      "end": 275.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were led by their evil nature",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 275.946,
      "end": 281.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they became wild, and ferocious, and a blood-thirsty people,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 281.42,
      "end": 284.299,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of idolatry and filthiness;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 284.479,
      "end": 287.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeding upon beasts of prey; dwelling in tents,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 287.956,
      "end": 290.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and wandering about in the wilderness",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 291.015,
      "end": 295.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with a short skin girdle about their loins and their heads shaven;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 295.235,
      "end": 299.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their skill was in the bow, and in the cimeter, and the ax.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 299.966,
      "end": 303.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many of them did eat nothing save it was raw meat;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 303.861,
      "end": 306.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were continually seeking to destroy us.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 307.235,
      "end": 311.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the people of Nephi did till the land,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 311.595,
      "end": 314.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and raise all manner of grain, and of fruit,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 314.329,
      "end": 315.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of herds,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 316.042,
      "end": 319.2,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of all manner of cattle of every kind,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 319.38,
      "end": 322.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goats, and wild goats, and also many horses.",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 323.497,
      "end": 326.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there were exceedingly many prophets among us.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 326.835,
      "end": 330.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people were a stiffnecked people, hard to understand.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 331.23,
      "end": 334.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was nothing save it was exceeding harshness,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 334.754,
      "end": 339.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "preaching and prophesying of wars, and contentions, and destructions,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 339.857,
      "end": 342.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continually reminding them of death,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 342.452,
      "end": 344.588,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the duration of eternity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 344.768,
      "end": 347.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the judgments and the power of God,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 347.409,
      "end": 350.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all these things\u2014stirring them up continually",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 350.468,
      "end": 353.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to keep them in the fear of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 353.434,
      "end": 356.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say there was nothing short of these things,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 356.54,
      "end": 359.234,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and exceedingly great plainness of speech,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 359.414,
      "end": 362.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "would keep them from going down speedily to destruction.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 363.123,
      "end": 366.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner do I write concerning them.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 367.1,
      "end": 371.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw wars between the Nephites and Lamanites in the course of my days.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 372.563,
      "end": 375.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I began to be old,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 375.437,
      "end": 378.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and an hundred and seventy and nine years had passed away",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 378.728,
      "end": 382.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that our father Lehi left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 383.495,
      "end": 386.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that I must soon go down to my grave,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 386.647,
      "end": 389.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having been wrought upon by the power of God",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 389.799,
      "end": 393.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I must preach and prophesy unto this people,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 393.323,
      "end": 396.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and declare the word according to the truth which is in Christ.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 396.847,
      "end": 399.169,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I have declared it in all my days,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 399.349,
      "end": 402.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have rejoiced in it above that of the world.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 403.048,
      "end": 405.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I soon go to the place of my rest,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 405.55,
      "end": 407.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is with my Redeemer;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 407.309,
      "end": 409.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that in him I shall rest.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 410.043,
      "end": 411.854,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I rejoice in the day",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 412.034,
      "end": 415.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when my mortal shall put on immortality,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 415.186,
      "end": 416.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall stand before him;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 416.991,
      "end": 419.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall I see his face with pleasure,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 419.493,
      "end": 421.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will say unto me:",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 421.298,
      "end": 423.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Come unto me, ye blessed,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 423.428,
      "end": 427.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there is a place prepared for you in the mansions of my Father.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 427.555,
      "end": 428.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 150
    }
  ]
}